{"tid":964494,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"繼KAI和Jennie  網瘋傳：D社還有4對情侶要爆！","createTime":"2019-01-01T10:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T02:08:18.000Z","uid":74065,"like":104,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"b6674a08894f396f22387d4673fd5743e05cc637","tid":964494,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:51:48.000Z","msg":"南韓媒體《Dispatch》每年1月1日都會爆出一對演藝圈情侶，2019年新春第一爆就是EXO成員Kai與BLACKPINK成員Jennie，兩人都是當紅偶像，消息震驚粉絲圈。不過這或許只是開頭，網路瘋傳神通廣大的「D社」，至少手頭上還有四對情侶要曝光。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3803/d3803824.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3803%2Fd3803824.jpg&h=ab3977e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲KAI和Jennie爆出戀情，成為2019年「元旦情侶」。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\nEXO Kai與BLACKPINK Jennie被拍到深夜在公園約會，兩人帶著同款不同色的情侶毛帽，手緊牽著彼此，Kai更把當天約會的照片上傳到Instagram，掌鏡人正是Jennie。SM娛樂也證實：「兩人是對彼此擁有好感的關係。」等同承認戀情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3803/d3803369.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3803%2Fd3803369.jpg&h=9530c8ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲KAI和Jennie同時間在巴黎，並都上傳了巴黎鐵塔的照片。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n不過隨後網路上也瘋傳小道消息，指總是精準掌握藝人戀愛消息的《Dispatch》，手頭上至少就還有4對明星情侶等著曝光。雖然消息並未得到證實，但由於《Dispatch》跟拍模式常採取「長期抗戰」，即使拍到鐵證也會等待時機才曝光消息，因此讓不少粉絲都表示既期待又怕受傷害，一方面好奇一方面也期待：「希望不是我家愛豆。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3803/d3803836.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3803%2Fd3803836.jpg&h=fe6764de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲網友爆料「D社」手頭上還有四對情侶要曝光。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n《Dispatch》近年來「成績斐然」，歷年來的元旦CP就包括2013年Rain和金泰熙、2014年潤娥和李昇基、2015年李政宰和名媛林世玲、2016年JYJ金俊秀與EXID成員Hani，以及2018年G-Dragon和前After School成員珠妍，以及2019年最新的KAI和Jennie，除了YG娛樂對戀情極少正面回應外，其他全都是承認戀愛中，命中率非常高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望快d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得一對個CLASS感覺太弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0be394c3bda74cedc6a198d94f7759189e838c","tid":964494,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:52:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4001a781d26de124704d1e66d3ebb40fb419076f","tid":964494,"uid":223790,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:52:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"733eb2bebd7e5b8bfab00e0bf41964edf83ab005","tid":964494,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T11:01:44.000Z","msg":"爆啦嘛 仲唔爆？"},{"pid":"fab2cd5d17718695206bf10f15395d209f05fc30","tid":964494,"uid":177639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T11:04:07.000Z","msg":"分4年爆"},{"pid":"698430cb0c91a1dfcbfcb37404aad8c7910f1c53","tid":964494,"uid":74065,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"quote":{"pid":"fab2cd5d17718695206bf10f15395d209f05fc30","tid":964494,"uid":177639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T11:04:07.000Z","msg":"分4年爆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T11:05:34.000Z","msg":"今年個對都冇乜味<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加多幾PAIR補返啦"},{"pid":"131bca37828ca62f93f838afa01fe4414008432b","tid":964494,"uid":171594,"like":176,"dislike":1,"score":175,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T11:06:25.000Z","msg":"同老楊爭女<br />\nKai死撚緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d661a96aa7ece366e782e2cc6ad316b2bc6968d","tid":964494,"uid":177639,"like":5,"dislike":23,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"698430cb0c91a1dfcbfcb37404aad8c7910f1c53","tid":964494,"uid":74065,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"quote":{"pid":"fab2cd5d17718695206bf10f15395d209f05fc30","tid":964494,"uid":177639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T11:04:07.000Z","msg":"分4年爆"},"ci